•
This weekend the Shop employees challenged the Innetech crew to a special Game of Skate tournament in the Pro Course.
—
The rules were simple; 
• 2 skaters from each crew 
• 3 games of skate 
 - One game on Flat
 - Two games on Pro Course obstacles 
—
With bragging rights (and lunch) on the line the two squads battled it out for SPoT supremacy...who did you have ur money on??!
—
Teams
Innetech: @rolo.c & @marsefarmer_ 
Shop Guys: @timgasiorski & @skatestoppers_ 
—
📱: @bowser_media_lab 
#SPoTSkateBattle #SPoTTeam #SPoTTampa

node.text:
The Tyshawn Jones signature shoe from Adidas Skateboarding is built with comfort in mind and feature a molded sockliner for outstanding board feel and an EVA midsole that cushions against impact. An abrasion-resistant toe holds up to hard riding. ⚫️⚪️

SPoT team rider @rolo.c hit the pro course in the new core black/footwear white colorway. Now available in store and online ⚫️⚪️

📹 @shailfish 

#adidasskateboarding #tyshawnjones #SPoTTampa
